txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Pure black fur from beasts surrounding Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'These will be used for crafting much for our people. Thank you.'
'The black fur from the creatures near Aughaire have many uses. If you deliver it to us, we will use what you find.'
Council of the North Task: Pure Black Fur
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of pure black fur to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the pure black fur to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver pure black fur from beasts surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: Pure black fur from beasts surrounding Aughaire.
